                    <div class="grid-item grid-item--header ">
                        <h2>Data Processing Agreement (“DPA”)</h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-s-100">


                    <div class="grid-item grid-item--text ">
                        <p>When you first engage with us we provide you with a contract that includes a Master Services Agreement, a Data Processing Agreement and a Statement of Work.</p>
                        <p>The Data Processing Agreement complies with Article 28. It outlines our commitment to processing data only as provided for in your instructions to us, to confidentiality, to security and to assist you in compliance with your obligations.</p>
                        <p>We will supply you with a sample Data Processing Agreement for the relevant service on request during our sales engagement with you.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="block grid white-bg    ">
        <div class="container ">
