                <div class="col col-s-100">

                    <div class="grid-item grid-item--header ">
                        <h2>Technical and Organisational Measures</h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-s-100">


                    <div class="grid-item grid-item--text ">
                        <p>We implement a variety of technical and organisational measures across our business and our service delivery in order to keep the personal data we process on your behalf secure.&nbsp;</p>
                        <p>These include:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li aria-level="1">All employees use encrypted devices.</li>
                            <li aria-level="1">All software we use in our service delivery has two factor authentication implemented by default.</li>
                            <li aria-level="1">We use a secure cloud-based file share to store our client data.&nbsp;</li>
                            <li aria-level="1">We implement a dedicated directory structure for each client so that client data is stored consistently, is easy to find and separate from other client’s data.</li>
                            <li aria-level="1">Files are not emailed internally or externally as email attachments, instead we send a link to the document(s)</li>
                            <li aria-level="1">We back-up our data regularly to a secure location, to a dedicated device that is stored in a locked facility with physical access controls.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="block grid white-bg    ">
